Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.70,0:00:01.69,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,{\i1}Darkness and Light!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:00:01.83,0:00:03.43,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,{\i1}Into the chaos of\nthe Feudal Era,{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:00:03.50,0:00:05.70,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,{\i1}the Sacred Jewel brings a\n{\i1}group of strangers together.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:00:05.94,0:00:08.93,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,{\i1}500 years across time,\ntheir destinies are controlled{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:00:09.01,0:00:11.20,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,{\i1}by the few remaining shards\nof the Jewel.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:00:11.91,0:00:13.14,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,{\i1}Feudal Fairy Tale:{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:00:13.21,0:00:14.11,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,{\i1}Inuyasha!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:00:14.71,0:00:17.44,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,{\i1}The frightening bird master, Princess Abi,\nsends her demon birds to attack the village.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:00:17.52,0:00:19.38,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,{\i1}But the holy one, St. Hijiri,\nstands in her way.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:00:19.45,0:00:22.36,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,{\i1}St. Hijiri, who was able to break through\NHakudoshi's barrier with a single arrow...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:00:22.36,0:00:24.22,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,{\i1}Could the true identity\nof this person... be Kikyo?!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:02:06.69,0:02:07.85,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,This {\i1}arrow....{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:02:09.76,0:02:12.79,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,{\i1}Inuyasha's Red Tetsusaiga could\nnot break through Hakudoshi's barrier,{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:02:12.87,0:02:14.33,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,{\i1}yet this arrow did...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:02:16.47,0:02:18.37,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,{\i1}Only one person is\ncapable of that...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:02:30.15,0:02:33.02,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,{\i1}Kikyo... is alive!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:02:34.42,0:02:35.94,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,It's not Kikyo.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:36.46,0:02:36.85,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:37.52,0:02:39.51,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,No one said anything.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:39.99,0:02:42.72,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,But you're all thinking it.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:44.06,0:02:46.62,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Even I wondered the\nsame thing.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:46.90,0:02:47.70,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,{\i1}However....{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:02:48.57,0:02:51.13,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,I don't get Kikyo's scent\nfrom this arrow.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:52.31,0:02:53.74,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,It's {\i1}different....{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:02:54.51,0:02:56.63,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,{\i1}What is this smell?{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:02:59.31,0:03:02.28,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,In any case, it's not the smell\nof any of our allies.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:02.72,0:03:04.58,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Not the smell of\nan ally?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:04.95,0:03:06.92,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Thinking about\nwhat you {\i1}said....{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:03:07.59,0:03:09.28,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,when that arrow was shot,
Dialogue: 0,0:03:09.52,0:03:12.49,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,I didn't sense Kikyo's\nspiritual powers.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:13.23,0:03:14.02,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,{\i1}Then....{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:03:14.33,0:03:15.56,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,who was it?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:16.50,0:03:18.93,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,That arrow helped Inuyasha.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:19.50,0:03:23.44,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Perhaps it was a friendly hand\nlent by St. Hijiri.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:23.77,0:03:24.74,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,That's right.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:25.17,0:03:26.60,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,That could be it.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:27.81,0:03:29.14,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,{\i1}St. Hijiri...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:03:30.41,0:03:32.81,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,We must hurry to\nthis St. Hijiri.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:33.28,0:03:35.25,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,The birds must be\nheaded that way, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:37.98,0:03:40.48,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,St. Hijiri, we are almost\nat the village.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:41.29,0:03:43.65,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,I hope they were\nable to hold out.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:05.04,0:04:07.60,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Everyone, do not move.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:13.12,0:04:15.38,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,W-Will we really be safe?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:15.49,0:04:18.08,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Won't they break through?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:18.32,0:04:20.69,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,When will St. Hijiri return?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:21.13,0:04:24.12,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Hah! A barrier?\NSuch insolence!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:26.47,0:04:29.06,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Quite strong for something\nerected by humans.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:29.37,0:04:32.36,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Then I'll force them\nto come out.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:35.17,0:04:36.23,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Go!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:45.72,0:04:48.24,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Aghh! The birds are aflame!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:48.65,0:04:50.32,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,We're surrounded by fire!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:50.52,0:04:52.65,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,We'll be burned alive!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:52.89,0:04:54.62,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,I can't take it anymore!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:54.86,0:04:56.16,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,This side's not burning.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:56.30,0:04:57.66,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Huh?! Let's make a run for it!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:58.70,0:05:01.57,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Do not leave the barrier.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:15.78,0:05:17.41,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,St. Hijiri has returned!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:17.48,0:05:19.18,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Please save us!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:21.05,0:05:22.99,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,{\i1}The one who erected\nthe barrier...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:05:24.12,0:05:25.28,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Slay him!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:38.40,0:05:39.03,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Huh?!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:41.11,0:05:42.77,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,We're saved!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:43.24,0:05:44.97,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,My {\i1}birds....are{\i0} gone!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:45.34,0:05:47.31,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Damn! What's going on?!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:48.18,0:05:49.48,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,{\i1}Ever since Naraku came\ninto the picture,{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:05:49.55,0:05:51.02,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,{\i1}I've had nothing but\ninterference!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:05:56.59,0:05:58.06,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,S-She's gone!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:58.72,0:06:00.66,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,It's the power of\NSt. Hijiri!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:00.76,0:06:01.92,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Thank you!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:01.99,0:06:04.33,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,You saved us, St. Hijiri!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:18.11,0:06:19.24,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,We passed the summit.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:19.41,0:06:21.97,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,We should reach St. Hijiri's\nvillage soon.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:24.58,0:06:28.92,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,{\i1}When we reach the village,\nwe may learn St. Hijiri's identity.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:06:31.19,0:06:32.18,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,There it is.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:32.36,0:06:33.09,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Yeah!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:35.86,0:06:37.99,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,I smell blood and\nsomething burning.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:38.23,0:06:38.99,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:39.37,0:06:41.89,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,It's coming from around\nthat craggy mountain.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:42.23,0:06:43.10,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Let's hurry!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:59.25,0:07:00.48,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,This {\i1}is....!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:07:02.09,0:07:04.39,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,St. Hijiri exterminated them.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:04.46,0:07:05.79,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,We're so grateful.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:07.06,0:07:12.16,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,He wiped out a whole flock\nof birds with a single arrow.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:13.37,0:07:15.03,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,{\i1}A single arrow?{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:07:18.14,0:07:20.83,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,And where is this\NSt. Hijiri?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:22.58,0:07:25.91,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,St. Hijiri has left\nthis area.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:26.18,0:07:26.74,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:27.45,0:07:31.51,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,He said he would find the\nbirds' nest and destroy them all.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:32.15,0:07:34.12,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,We are ever so thankful.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:35.02,0:07:37.82,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Seems we just missed him.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:40.13,0:07:40.99,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,{\i1}Inuyasha....{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:07:41.96,0:07:43.29,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Should we go after him?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:44.40,0:07:46.86,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,After this St. Hijiri?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:47.83,0:07:51.29,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,It could be Kikyo, you know.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:54.84,0:07:55.90,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,{\i1}Kagome....{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:08:02.58,0:08:03.45,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,{\i1}Inuyasha...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:08:06.75,0:08:09.52,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,{\i1}Kikyo... was killed by Naraku.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:08:10.49,0:08:11.08,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,{\i1}But...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:08:12.56,0:08:15.22,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,{\i1}I didn't see Kikyo die.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:08:16.10,0:08:17.12,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,{\i1}Nor did I see her body.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:08:18.73,0:08:21.60,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,{\i1}But Kikyo... if you are alive,{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:08:21.67,0:08:23.64,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,{\i1}why haven't you shown\nyourself to me?{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:08:29.84,0:08:30.97,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,{\i1}Kagome....{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:08:39.65,0:08:42.38,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Kagome is so brave.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:42.99,0:08:44.96,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,How is she able to\nspeak up like {\i1}that....?{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:08:45.16,0:08:46.85,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,You mean, about Kikyo?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:47.56,0:08:51.09,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,If St. Hijiri turns out\nto be Kikyo,
Dialogue: 0,0:08:51.16,0:08:52.69,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,we're sure to cross paths\nat some point.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:53.33,0:08:56.53,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,If her aim is to find\nthe birds' nest.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:57.34,0:08:58.86,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Yes, {\i1}but....{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:08:59.81,0:09:02.40,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Inuyasha becomes so indecisive\nwhenever he sees {\i1}her....{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:09:02.74,0:09:05.01,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,And each time, Kagome\nhas forgiven him.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:07.58,0:09:09.95,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,If it were me, I'd push him\nover some cliff,
Dialogue: 0,0:09:10.02,0:09:11.64,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,and make him a cripple.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:12.82,0:09:14.91,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Are you talking about me?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:16.82,0:09:17.72,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,She's serious!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:21.46,0:09:23.59,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Kagome, you okay with this?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:24.00,0:09:24.89,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,With what?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:25.56,0:09:26.72,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Besides, what about you?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:27.87,0:09:30.39,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,If St. Hijiri turns out\nto be {\i1}Kikyo....{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:09:35.54,0:09:36.44,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,I {\i1}dunno....{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:09:36.64,0:09:37.11,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,{\i1}Huh....{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:09:38.51,0:09:40.10,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,{\i1}He's so honest.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:09:40.98,0:09:41.67,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,{\i1}But....{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:09:42.31,0:09:43.68,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,But if that's {\i1}true....{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:09:44.08,0:09:47.28,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,it'll mean that Naraku failed\nto kill Kikyo.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:49.96,0:09:51.58,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,{\i1}And that means...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:09:51.66,0:09:54.29,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,{\i1}he'll come and try to\nkill her once more.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:09:56.66,0:09:58.13,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,In any case, we'll just\nconcentrate on
Dialogue: 0,0:09:58.20,0:10:01.17,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,finding the birds' nest and\ndestroying them.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:01.37,0:10:01.86,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:11.41,0:10:13.44,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Damn! Just who are {\i1}you....?{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:10:13.95,0:10:15.91,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,to be able to break\nthrough my barrier?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:16.95,0:10:18.94,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,{\i1}Such a stubborn kid!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:10:24.62,0:10:25.28,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Huh?!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:29.66,0:10:30.92,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,{\i1}Am I really seeing this?!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:10:31.46,0:10:33.26,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,{\i1}No, this kid...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:10:34.87,0:10:36.86,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,{\i1}I can hear his heart,{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:10:36.97,0:10:38.99,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,{\i1}but he's hollow\ninside.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:10:40.67,0:10:43.77,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,{\i1}Is his heart...\nsomewhere else?{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:10:49.21,0:10:50.34,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Mistress Kaede!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:50.42,0:10:52.01,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Mistress Kaede!\NTerrible news!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:53.02,0:10:54.28,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,What is it?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:54.69,0:10:55.71,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,{\i1}Well....{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:10:57.69,0:10:59.95,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,What?! Is that true?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:00.33,0:11:01.16,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Yes!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:01.99,0:11:04.79,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,And where did you see\nthis suspicious light?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:05.16,0:11:07.72,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,We just saw it\nfalling from the {\i1}sky....{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:11:08.33,0:11:11.10,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,towards our lady Kikyo's shrine.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:11.64,0:11:12.43,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,What?!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:15.61,0:11:16.47,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,There it is!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:17.71,0:11:18.51,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:21.68,0:11:22.94,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,{\i1}W-What....{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:11:23.18,0:11:24.27,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Demons?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:25.82,0:11:27.88,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Mistress Kaede,\nwhat were they?!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:29.82,0:11:31.55,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,{\i1}Hmm....{\i0} They weren't demons.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:31.79,0:11:34.85,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,They were probably {\i1}shikigami{\i0}\nmessengers sent by someone.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:35.56,0:11:38.53,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,{\i1}I did not sense any\nevil aura from them.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:11:39.30,0:11:40.16,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Mistress Kaede!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:40.30,0:11:40.86,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:41.30,0:11:42.49,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Take a look at this!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:42.80,0:11:43.56,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,What is it?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:44.40,0:11:46.43,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,It looks like they\ndug here.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:46.61,0:11:47.33,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,What?!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:47.87,0:11:53.11,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Once before, Kikyo's ashes\nand dirt from her grave were taken.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:53.21,0:11:54.37,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Not again!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:55.78,0:11:59.77,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,{\i1}Who would take soil from\NSister Kikyo's grave?!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:11:59.92,0:12:01.82,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,{\i1}For what purpose?{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:12:07.16,0:12:08.96,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Naraku's demons?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:09.43,0:12:11.69,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,They seem to be\nlooking for something.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:12.03,0:12:12.76,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,{\i1}Uh-huh....{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:12:12.93,0:12:15.20,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Probably looking\nfor St. {\i1}Hijiri....{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:12:15.33,0:12:18.67,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,You're right. For Naraku,\nhe poses a problem.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:20.07,0:12:21.77,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,{\i1}So Naraku realizes this\nas well?{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:12:23.48,0:12:25.77,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,{\i1}That St. Hijiri may\nbe Kikyo...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:12:27.28,0:12:28.25,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,{\i1}If so...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:12:28.88,0:12:31.48,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,{\i1}Does he intend to find her\nand kill her again?{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:12:35.12,0:12:36.52,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,St. {\i1}Hijiri....{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:12:37.49,0:12:39.79,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,We've heard rumors.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:40.29,0:12:42.85,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,We heard that he\nwas seen hereabouts.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:43.30,0:12:44.06,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,I {\i1}dunno....{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:12:44.30,0:12:47.49,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,But it could be a\nsign from him.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:47.97,0:12:50.96,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Just before dawn, two\nstrange streaks of light
Dialogue: 0,0:12:51.04,0:12:52.40,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,appeared in the sky.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:53.41,0:12:56.27,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,And they were sucked\ninto the forbidden mountain.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:58.04,0:12:59.67,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,"Forbidden"?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:00.51,0:13:04.51,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,{\i1}Yeah....{\i0} Only the selected\nmay enter.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:05.12,0:13:06.95,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Shall we go, Inuyasha?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:07.62,0:13:10.42,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,{\i1}Yeah....{\i0} Besides, we have\nnothing else to go on.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:15.56,0:13:19.52,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Weren't we looking for\nthe birds' nest?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:19.93,0:13:20.42,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:20.93,0:13:23.49,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Somewhere along the way,
Dialogue: 0,0:13:23.57,0:13:27.23,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,that goal seems to have changed\nto meeting this St. Hijiri.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:27.81,0:13:31.57,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Shippo, don't say things like\nthat in front of Kagome.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:31.74,0:13:34.80,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Kagome probably noticed\nthat already.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:35.75,0:13:36.71,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,It's that mountain.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:38.52,0:13:41.65,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Inuyasha, something\nis {\i1}sparkling....{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:13:42.29,0:13:43.02,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Water maybe?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:43.09,0:13:44.99,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Yeah, could be a waterfall.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:06.18,0:14:07.11,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,{\i1}Demons....{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:14:07.31,0:14:09.04,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,They're looking for St. Hijiri.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:11.72,0:14:13.65,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Inuyasha, have you\nnoticed them?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:13.89,0:14:16.38,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,You mean Naraku's demons?\NYeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:16.86,0:14:18.85,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,They're following us, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:19.39,0:14:20.12,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,{\i1}Or....{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:14:20.66,0:14:22.29,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,There're more and more of them!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:23.33,0:14:27.42,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,It seems they're all heading\ntoward the forbidden mountain.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:28.50,0:14:30.09,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,{\i1}Does that mean Kikyo is there?{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:14:38.38,0:14:39.07,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,What the.!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:39.34,0:14:40.44,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,A sacred arrow!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:40.61,0:14:42.71,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,So, St. Hijiri is here\nin this mountain!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:45.58,0:14:46.38,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Let's go!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:05.57,0:15:07.27,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,T-They're coming from below!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:11.31,0:15:12.28,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Hiraikotsu!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:13.98,0:15:14.78,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Move!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:19.42,0:15:20.51,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,{\i1}This is no good!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:15:20.99,0:15:23.68,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Miroku! Sango!\NTake care of Kagome!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:23.76,0:15:24.28,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:29.33,0:15:30.30,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Go on ahead, everyone!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:30.36,0:15:31.89,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Inuyasha, what're {\i1}you....!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:15:32.06,0:15:33.16,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Isn't it obvious?!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:34.97,0:15:37.33,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,After I destroy these vermin,\NI'll follow you!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:37.80,0:15:39.96,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Go and find this St. Hijiri!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:40.24,0:15:40.73,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:41.44,0:15:42.30,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Go on!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:42.84,0:15:43.50,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Kirara!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:46.61,0:15:47.70,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,{\i1}Inuyasha!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:15:48.35,0:15:51.01,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,{\i1}Is it okay for us to\nsee him first?{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:15:51.58,0:15:54.52,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,{\i1}If St. Hijiri is really Kikyo...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:15:56.82,0:15:58.19,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,{\i1}I don't know...\nwhat I'll do.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:16:00.13,0:16:00.99,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,{\i1}But...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:16:04.73,0:16:07.06,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Wind Scar!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:16.07,0:16:17.74,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,{\i1}I have to meet him and\nsee for myself...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:16:19.08,0:16:20.57,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,{\i1}Or I won't be able\nto get on with my life.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:16:31.66,0:16:33.52,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,{\i1}Is that Kikyo?{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:16:35.63,0:16:38.46,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,{\i1}I don't get Kikyo's\nscent from him.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:16:41.33,0:16:42.30,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,{\i1}But...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:16:43.97,0:16:46.77,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Your face! Let me see your face!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:54.78,0:16:57.21,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,I wonder if Inuyasha will be okay?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:57.68,0:16:59.17,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,He'll come after us\nas soon as he's done.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:00.49,0:17:01.38,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,{\i1}She's right.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:17:02.22,0:17:06.12,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,{\i1}Inuyasha is the one\nwho most wants to meet St. Hijiri.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:17:09.06,0:17:09.82,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Sango!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:10.20,0:17:11.63,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,More demons!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:17.97,0:17:19.44,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Kagome, {\i1}Shippo....{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:17:19.64,0:17:20.40,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Stay here!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:20.47,0:17:20.90,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Uh-huh!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:20.97,0:17:21.56,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Kirara!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:25.01,0:17:25.67,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Hiraikotsu!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:27.18,0:17:30.77,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,{\i1}K-Kagome....{\i0}\nl-I'm with you!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:31.32,0:17:31.87,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Uh-huh!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:32.45,0:17:33.94,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,I must be strong!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:36.66,0:17:38.59,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,K-Kagome....demons!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:40.83,0:17:42.09,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Huh?\NWhat's that?!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:42.99,0:17:44.15,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Soul Collectors!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:45.80,0:17:48.03,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,K-Kagome!\NWhere are you going?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:48.67,0:17:50.13,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,{\i1}So Kikyo really is...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:17:53.00,0:17:53.87,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Kagome!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:54.37,0:17:55.60,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,I'm going after them!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:55.77,0:17:57.21,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Kikyo may be there!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:57.58,0:17:59.31,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Wait! Don't be so hasty!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:04.38,0:18:05.78,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,S-She disappeared!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:06.08,0:18:07.14,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,A {\i1}barrier....{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:18:08.25,0:18:11.31,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Answer! Are you Kikyo or not?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:12.42,0:18:14.65,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,A potent aura has\nravaged her flesh.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:15.63,0:18:17.69,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Her body cannot\nbe restored to its original form.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:18.36,0:18:19.92,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,She also lost her voice.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:21.37,0:18:23.39,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,She fights with her\nspirit alone.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:24.20,0:18:25.07,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,{\i1}However....{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:18:25.77,0:18:27.36,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,soon her strength\nwill run out.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:28.04,0:18:29.01,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,{\i1}Back then...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:18:30.18,0:18:31.47,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,{\i1}She didn't die?{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:18:34.41,0:18:35.14,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Kikyo!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:35.98,0:18:37.28,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,You are Kikyo!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:40.42,0:18:41.48,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Kikyo!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:45.49,0:18:46.18,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Huh?!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:48.56,0:18:50.03,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Kikyo!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:53.03,0:18:53.90,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Kikyo!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:18.02,0:19:18.49,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:22.43,0:19:23.33,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,This {\i1}is....{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:19:23.53,0:19:24.52,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,A paper doll?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:24.63,0:19:27.79,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Damn that Kikyo\nis elusive!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:29.67,0:19:30.33,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Kagura!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:30.67,0:19:32.53,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,What's going on?!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:32.84,0:19:34.53,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,That's my question.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:34.77,0:19:36.33,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Sending me on\na fool's errand!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:37.31,0:19:39.40,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Is Kikyo alive?!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:40.21,0:19:42.74,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,{\i1}Hmm....{\i0}\NAt least Naraku thinks so.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:43.58,0:19:46.07,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,The arrow that broke\nthrough Hakudoshi's barrier
Dialogue: 0,0:19:46.45,0:19:50.15,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,had dirt from Onigumo's\ncave on its arrowhead.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:50.62,0:19:52.72,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Huh? {\i1}Onigumo....?{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:19:53.59,0:19:56.53,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,{\i1}So that was the scent\nfrom that arrow...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:19:59.33,0:20:03.83,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,The soil there is infused\nwith Onigumo's longing for Kikyo.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:05.20,0:20:08.54,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,And that protects Kikyo\nfrom Naraku.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:09.21,0:20:12.61,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Kikyo is the only one who\ncan benefit from Onigumi's dirt.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:14.61,0:20:18.52,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,In any case, we've been\nchasing around after a fake.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:19.25,0:20:19.84,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,See ya!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:22.49,0:20:25.01,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,{\i1}Naraku's most troublesome hindrance\nis still alive...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:20:26.12,0:20:28.25,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,{\i1}Hah... this is starting\nto get very interesting.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:20:36.70,0:20:39.30,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Those two have also {\i1}disappeared....{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:20:55.62,0:20:57.11,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,{\i1}Is Kikyo really...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:21:04.63,0:21:07.66,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,{\i1}Kikyo... is alive somewhere.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:21:28.65,0:21:31.05,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Are they calling to me?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:37.46,0:21:38.09,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Huh?!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:43.40,0:21:44.46,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,A {\i1}waterfall....{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:21:48.57,0:21:49.27,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Huh?!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:57.92,0:21:59.14,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,{\i1}Kikyo...!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:23:45.42,0:23:47.25,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,When I was alone at\nthe base of the mountain,
Dialogue: 0,0:23:47.33,0:23:48.55,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,I met St. Hijiri!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:48.83,0:23:51.26,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,It was actually a\npaper doll controlled by Kikyo.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:51.73,0:23:53.56,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,The real Kikyo is submerged\n{\i1}underwater....{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:23:54.10,0:23:54.93,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Is she alive?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:55.13,0:23:55.79,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,{\i1}Or....{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:23:56.13,0:23:57.00,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Please {\i1}choose....{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:23:57.50,0:23:59.06,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,if you will save her or not.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:59.37,0:24:00.70,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,You are the only one
Dialogue: 0,0:24:00.77,0:24:01.76,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,who can save her.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:01.91,0:24:02.87,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Right now, you {\i1}hold....{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:24:02.94,0:24:04.88,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,her life in your hands.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:05.88,0:24:09.14,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Next on Inuyasha:\N"Kagome's Instinctive Choice"
Dialogue: 0,0:24:09.48,0:24:10.85,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Only I can save her?
Dialogue: 0,0:24:11.08,0:24:12.38,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,That's why you're telling\nme to choose?
